is because they're trying to cleanse Gaza.

18:08.160 --> 18:11.320
It's very important to understand that.

18:11.320 --> 18:13.040
And then finally, what they're doing

18:13.080 --> 18:15.520
is starving the population.

18:15.520 --> 18:18.960
There's all sorts of talk about famine in the north,

18:18.960 --> 18:20.360
northern part of Gaza.

18:20.360 --> 18:24.040
The United States is leaning heavily on the Israelis

18:24.040 --> 18:26.680
to let food and other kinds of aid in.

18:26.680 --> 18:30.080
The Israelis are resisting at every turn.

18:30.080 --> 18:32.080
Why are they starving the Palestinians?

18:32.080 --> 18:34.160
Why are they killing the Palestinians?

18:34.160 --> 18:36.240
Why are they making Gaza unlivable?

18:36.240 --> 18:37.080
It's very simple.

18:37.080 --> 18:38.400
They wanna drive them out.

18:39.400 --> 18:45.080
So that's basically what's been happening.

18:45.080 --> 18:47.600
And in the beginning, right,

18:47.600 --> 18:50.080
there was all sorts of talk about genocide.

18:50.080 --> 18:54.120
