18:54.120 --> 18:56.400
is saying this is not a genocide.

18:56.400 --> 18:59.040
But after December, I changed my mind on that.

18:59.040 --> 19:02.040
I think the Israelis are now engaged in genocide.

19:02.040 --> 19:03.840
And what's happened here

19:03.840 --> 19:05.600
is because they have been unable

19:05.600 --> 19:08.040
to get the Palestinians out.

19:08.040 --> 19:09.480
They've had to increase

19:09.480 --> 19:12.640
the amount of killing that they do, right?

19:12.640 --> 19:15.560
They're continuing to push

19:15.560 --> 19:18.160
to get the Palestinians out of Gaza.

19:18.160 --> 19:21.400
And the way they do that is just kill more and more people

19:21.400 --> 19:23.560
and make the Palestinian,

19:23.560 --> 19:28.800
make the situation in Gaza more and more unlivable, right?

19:28.800 --> 19:31.880
So the situation's just getting worse and worse and worse.

19:31.880 --> 19:33.760
Despite the fact that the United States

19:33.760 --> 19:36.560
and actually the West more generally doing what they can,

19:38.520 --> 19:41.320
help feed the Palestinians.

19:43.520 --> 19:46.080
So the question is, where are we today?

19:46.080 --> 19:47.120
Where are we today?

19:49.040 --> 19:52.040
First of all, they've not defeated Hamas

19:52.040 --> 19:53.720
and they're not gonna defeat Hamas.

19:53.720 --> 19:56.520
Kurt Campbell, who is the deputy secretary of state

19:56.520 --> 19:58.360
basically said that yesterday.

19:58.360 --> 20:01.200
There are all sorts of stories in the Israeli press

20:01.200 --> 20:03.920
that they're not gonna defeat Hamas.

20:03.920 --> 20:06.160
They haven't gotten the hostages back

20:07.120 --> 20:12.120
and they have not been able to cleanse Gaza.

20:14.360 --> 20:16.600
They've not been able to cleanse Gaza.

20:16.600 --> 20:18.720
Furthermore, they're stuck in Gaza.

20:19.640 --> 20:21.760
They're there, right?

20:21.760 --> 20:24.580
They got out in 2005 and they're back there.

20:25.920 --> 20:26.960
This is not good.

20:29.400 --> 20:33.760
So what you see here is that Israel is in real trouble

20:34.640 --> 20:35.480
in Gaza.

20:36.920 --> 20:40.160
Now, in addition to the problem in Gaza,

20:40.160 --> 20:42.600
they have a huge problem with Hezbollah

20:42.600 --> 20:47.240
because Hezbollah in the North in support of Hamas

20:47.240 --> 20:49.960
has been shelling Northern Israel.

20:49.960 --> 20:52.840
And there are somewhere between 60,000

20:52.840 --> 20:57.200
and 100,000 Israelis from the Northern part of Israel

20:57.200 --> 21:00.080
who have had to move into the center of Israel

21:00.080 --> 21:03.200
on a temporary basis and can't go home

21:03.200 --> 21:07.880
because Hezbollah is shelling Northern Israel.

21:07.880 --> 21:12.880
And Hezbollah has said that until this all ends in Gaza,

21:14.480 --> 21:16.920
they're gonna continue to fight the Israelis.

21:16.920 --> 21:19.000
This is a huge problem for the Israelis.

21:19.000 --> 21:21.520
So they not only have trouble with Hamas and Gaza,

21:21.520 --> 21:25.400
they have trouble with Hezbollah up on the Northern border.

21:25.400 --> 21:28.880
And by the way, the Houthis are actually now taking aim

21:28.880 --> 21:32.000
at the Israelis and the Houthis just recently landed

21:32.000 --> 21:37.000
their first missile inside of Israel.

21:38.600 --> 21:42.160
Just one, but that's a harbinger of things to come.

21:43.000 --> 21:46.200
You see how much trouble Israel is in.

21:46.200 --> 21:48.920
They have not achieved their objectives

21:50.040 --> 21:52.240
with regard to those two stated objectives

21:52.240 --> 21:55.920
and with regard to the ethnic cleansing.

21:55.920 --> 21:57.320
And as I said to you before,

21:57.320 --> 22:00.600
you always wanna understand there are four options here.

22:00.640 --> 22:02.120
First two are off the table

22:02.120 --> 22:06.040
and that comes down to apartheid or ethnic cleansing.

22:06.040 --> 22:08.240
And the Israelis understand full well.

22:08.240 --> 22:12.920
In apartheid state, we remember what happened to South Africa.

22:12.920 --> 22:15.360
We have got to solve that problem.

22:15.360 --> 22:17.960
That's why ethnic cleansing is so attractive,

22:17.960 --> 22:22.000
but they've been unable to ethnically cleanse so far.

22:22.000 --> 22:23.000
That's that story.

22:23.000 --> 22:25.360
That's the story about Gaza.

22:25.360 --> 22:27.760
Let's shift gears now and talk about Iran

22:28.200 --> 22:32.240
versus Israel versus the United States.

22:34.200 --> 22:39.200
Up until April 1st, the war between Israel and Iran

22:40.560 --> 22:44.480
and even the United States and Iran was a shadow war.

22:46.640 --> 22:48.880
And it's very important to understand

22:48.880 --> 22:53.880
that we did not want the war, that shadow war to escalate.

22:54.320 --> 22:57.120
We did not wanna see Iran and Israel

22:57.120 --> 22:59.000
get into a fight.

22:59.000 --> 23:02.640
Very important to understand, nor did the Iranians.

23:02.640 --> 23:05.640
The Iranians had no interest in escalation.

23:05.640 --> 23:08.520
The country that had an interest in escalation

23:08.520 --> 23:09.680
were the Israelis.

23:09.680 --> 23:12.160
The Israelis have had their gun sights on Iran

23:12.160 --> 23:15.120
for a long time and they've been doing everything

23:15.120 --> 23:19.520
they can over time to pull us into a war against Iran,

23:19.520 --> 23:21.600
but we didn't want a war.

23:21.600 --> 23:25.600
What happens on April 1st, as I'm sure all of you remember,

23:25.600 --> 23:30.600
is that the Israelis hit the Iranian embassy

23:31.560 --> 23:33.520
in Damascus, Syria.

23:34.680 --> 23:39.680
This drives the Iranians a portray

23:42.080 --> 23:44.800
and the Iranians make it clear

23:44.800 --> 23:49.800
that they're going to retaliate against Israel.

23:50.000 --> 23:54.120
The United States is a guest.

23:54.120 --> 23:56.560
The United States is very angry at the Israelis

23:56.560 --> 24:01.000
for doing this and not telling them that it was coming.

24:01.000 --> 24:06.000
So the Israelis look like they're gonna get a big conflict

24:06.920 --> 24:08.440
between Israel and the United States

24:08.440 --> 24:10.960
on one side and the Iranians on the other side,

24:10.960 --> 24:12.760
but the United States doesn't want this

24:12.760 --> 24:14.960
and Iran doesn't want this.

24:14.960 --> 24:19.960
So what happens, this is April 1st, the attack on the embassy.

24:20.240 --> 24:25.240
On April 14th, Iran retaliates against Israel.

24:25.760 --> 24:27.520
You all remember this.

24:27.520 --> 24:30.560
The question is what happens between April 1st

24:30.560 --> 24:34.680
and April 14th and then what happens on April 14th?

24:34.680 --> 24:37.920
So very important to understand these details.

24:37.920 --> 24:42.920
The United States and Iran work together

24:43.480 --> 24:44.880
through intermediaries,

24:44.880 --> 24:47.400
because we don't have direct relations.

24:47.520 --> 24:51.600
We work together through intermediaries

24:51.600 --> 24:56.600
to make sure that the Iranian attack is limited,

24:57.000 --> 25:01.120
that we see it coming beforehand

25:01.120 --> 25:04.640
and that the United States and the Israelis

25:04.640 --> 25:08.160
and others are able to deal with the attack.

25:08.160 --> 25:11.720
Furthermore, we make it clear that we want the Iranians

25:11.720 --> 25:14.720
not to hit any populated areas

25:14.720 --> 25:18.560
and to basically go after one or two military targets.

25:18.560 --> 25:21.560
We and the Iranians agree

25:21.560 --> 25:24.000
that it will be a limited attack.

25:24.880 --> 25:26.960
We're coordinating with the Iranians

25:26.960 --> 25:28.800
because again, we don't want escalation.

25:28.800 --> 25:31.800
We meaning the Americans, nor do they.

25:31.800 --> 25:36.800
Then when the Iranian attack comes, a hotline,

25:37.760 --> 25:42.800
an informal hotline is set up between the United States

25:42.800 --> 25:46.560
and Iran via Oman,

25:47.480 --> 25:50.000
because both the Iranians and the Americans

25:50.000 --> 25:53.440
wanna keep this one under control.

25:53.440 --> 25:55.800
Very important to understand that.

25:55.800 --> 26:00.800
And the Iranians attack and what happens there?

26:02.280 --> 26:07.280
The Americans are deeply involved in defending Israel.

26:07.280 --> 26:09.440
You all remember, everybody talked about

26:09.440 --> 26:12.240
how the Jordanians, the Saudis, the French,

26:12.240 --> 26:14.360
the British, the Americans, the Israelis,

26:14.360 --> 26:18.440
they were all involved in dealing with this attack.

26:18.440 --> 26:20.080
This is a real problem for Israel

26:20.080 --> 26:22.520
because Israel has always prided itself

26:22.520 --> 26:26.680
on being able to independently deal with an adversary

26:26.680 --> 26:28.640
that thinks about attacking it.

26:28.640 --> 26:31.200
Well, in this case, right,

26:31.200 --> 26:35.080
not only are we coordinating things with the Iranians

26:35.080 --> 26:36.760
to make sure this is limited

26:36.760 --> 26:39.400
and it doesn't spin out of control,

26:39.400 --> 26:42.480
but there is considerable evidence

26:42.480 --> 26:47.000
that roughly half of the missiles and drones

26:47.000 --> 26:50.520
that were shot down were shot down by the United States,

26:50.520 --> 26:53.840
not by Israel, roughly half.

26:53.840 --> 26:56.080
We were deeply involved.

26:56.080 --> 27:00.400
We had naval ships that shot down Iranian ballistic missiles

27:00.400 --> 27:02.200
and we were using fighter aircraft

27:02.200 --> 27:07.200
to shoot down cruise missiles and shoot down drones.

27:07.200 --> 27:10.360
Now, the Israelis played a very important role in this,

27:10.360 --> 27:12.440
but it's important to understand

27:12.440 --> 27:14.200
we, the United States of America,

27:14.200 --> 27:16.120
were coordinating the effort.

27:16.120 --> 27:17.720
See how deeply involved we were?

27:17.720 --> 27:19.960
We wanted to keep this one under control.

27:19.960 --> 27:21.120
We wanted to make sure

27:21.120 --> 27:23.720
that that Iranian offensive against Israel

27:23.720 --> 27:25.680
was not successful.

27:25.680 --> 27:28.080
That brings me to the final part of the story

27:28.080 --> 27:32.520
about April events involving Iran and Israel.

27:32.520 --> 27:35.760
The Israelis retaliate on April 19th.

27:35.760 --> 27:39.680
Remember, April 1st is when they hit the embassy in Damascus.

27:39.680 --> 27:44.680
April 14th is when Iran goes after Israel,

27:45.640 --> 27:50.040
does limited damage, hardly any damage,

27:50.040 --> 27:54.280
and then on April 19th, the Israelis retaliate.

27:54.280 --> 27:55.320
Now, as you would expect,

27:55.320 --> 27:58.240
the Israelis wanted to unleash the dogs.

27:58.240 --> 28:02.320
The Israelis wanted a big counterattack on Iran.

28:02.320 --> 28:06.400
The United States did not want that for one second.

28:06.400 --> 28:09.040
We were trying to put a cap on the volcano.

28:09.040 --> 28:12.000
So what the Israelis end up doing

28:12.000 --> 28:16.760
is basically taking out one radar

28:16.760 --> 28:21.760
in the Isfahan area of Iran, just one radar.

28:22.640 --> 28:25.480
It's a radar associated with an S-300 missile.

28:25.480 --> 28:30.480
It is a very, very limited response.

28:31.320 --> 28:33.640
And it's a limited response

28:33.640 --> 28:36.720
because the United States demands

28:36.720 --> 28:38.680
that it be a limited response.

28:38.680 --> 28:41.120
Furthermore, we go to great lengths to tell the Israelis

28:41.120 --> 28:46.120
they actually won a great victory on April 14th

28:46.320 --> 28:51.320
by stopping all those Israeli missiles and drones.

28:52.400 --> 28:55.160
So Israel, except the fact

28:55.160 --> 28:58.000
that you won a great victory on April 14th,

28:58.000 --> 29:01.680
all we need is just a small-scale attack

29:01.680 --> 29:03.280
where we go after one radar,

29:03.280 --> 29:05.160
and that's the end of the story.

29:05.160 --> 29:07.960
And of course, that was the end of the story.

29:07.960 --> 29:08.920
This one went away,

29:08.920 --> 29:12.920
unlike Gaza, which continues on to this day.

29:12.920 --> 29:15.800
So what I'm telling you is you have these two big conflicts,

29:15.800 --> 29:18.560
the one in Gaza, which I just described,

29:18.560 --> 29:21.920
and then the one involving Iran, Israel,

29:21.920 --> 29:25.480
and the United States between April 1st and April 19th.

29:26.480 --> 29:31.160
Now, I want to talk about the consequences of this

29:31.160 --> 29:35.720
for Israel, United States, and Iran.

29:35.720 --> 29:37.320
And as I said to you,

29:37.320 --> 29:41.880
I believe that Israel was the big loser here.

29:41.880 --> 29:44.760
Now, you're saying to yourself, why is that the case?

29:45.760 --> 29:47.680
Number of reasons.

29:47.680 --> 29:52.320
First of all, the Israelis are back in Gaza.

29:53.080 --> 29:55.440
They got out in 2005.

29:55.440 --> 29:58.840
Ariel Sharon, as you all know, is no shrinking violet.

30:00.120 --> 30:04.600
He's at least as tough an ombre as Benjamin Netanyahu.

30:04.600 --> 30:08.440
He pulled out because Gaza's a hornet's nest.

30:08.440 --> 30:12.600
Well, the Israelis are back in Gaza.

30:12.600 --> 30:17.600
They have no way of getting out at the moment,

30:18.600 --> 30:23.600
and they have no solution to the problem.

30:23.920 --> 30:26.280
They've made Gaza unlivable.

30:26.280 --> 30:27.880
What are they going to do?

30:27.880 --> 30:30.440
The Palestinians are not leaving.

30:30.440 --> 30:31.600
What are they going to do?

30:31.600 --> 30:33.200
They're running the place.

30:34.320 --> 30:35.800
They're in deep trouble.

30:37.600 --> 30:40.960
Second reason the Israelis lose,

30:40.960 --> 30:45.240
you have to understand how the Israelis think about deterrence.

30:45.800 --> 30:48.280
And this is a very smart way of thinking about deterrence.

30:48.280 --> 30:50.720
I'm not being critical of Israeli thinking here.

30:52.720 --> 30:56.600
What the Israelis believe is that their deterrence

30:56.600 --> 31:01.600
depends on escalation dominance, escalation dominance.

31:01.960 --> 31:06.960
That means if somebody whacks me and I whacked them back,

31:07.480 --> 31:12.320
I whacked them back harder than they initially whacked me.

31:12.320 --> 31:15.920
In other words, as we go up the escalation ladder,

31:15.920 --> 31:19.260
I dominate escalation dominance.

31:19.260 --> 31:24.260
The best example of this is in the summer of 2003,

31:25.840 --> 31:30.840
Hezbollah killed a few Israelis,

31:31.080 --> 31:32.520
this is up on the northern border.

31:32.520 --> 31:35.360
Hezbollah killed a few Israelis

31:35.360 --> 31:39.360
and kidnapped an Israeli, okay?

31:39.400 --> 31:43.240
The Israelis massively retaliated.

31:43.240 --> 31:46.320
And Nasrallah, who is the head of Hezbollah,

31:46.320 --> 31:49.300
said, I think two months later,

31:49.300 --> 31:52.920
Nasrallah said, if I had known

31:52.920 --> 31:57.080
what the Israelis were gonna do in terms of retaliating,

31:57.080 --> 32:02.080
I would have never allowed the attack on July 12th, 2006.

32:04.400 --> 32:07.760
That's escalation dominance, do you understand?

32:07.760 --> 32:10.320
It's very important, from Israel's point of view,

32:10.320 --> 32:12.920
they have to make it clear to all their neighbors

32:12.920 --> 32:16.680
that if you whack us, we'll whack you back harder.

32:16.680 --> 32:20.840
It's now very clear the Israelis no longer

32:20.840 --> 32:25.120
have escalation dominance vis-a-vis Iran

32:25.120 --> 32:28.520
or vis-a-vis Hezbollah.

32:28.520 --> 32:31.720
They cannot shut down the conflict

32:31.720 --> 32:34.640
with Hezbollah on their northern border.

32:34.640 --> 32:36.280
Really quite remarkable.

32:36.280 --> 32:40.120
The Israelis are hitting Hezbollah very hard

32:40.120 --> 32:43.240
and Hezbollah is responding.

32:43.240 --> 32:48.240
Hezbollah has 150,000 rockets and missiles

32:48.400 --> 32:52.400
and those numbers will only grow at the passage of time.

32:52.400 --> 32:55.280
150,000, right?

32:55.280 --> 32:57.440
So the Israelis are limited in what they can do.

32:57.440 --> 33:00.000
And with regard to Iran, I described to you

33:00.000 --> 33:03.960
what happened April 1st, April 14th, April 19th.

33:04.000 --> 33:06.600
That is not escalation dominance.

33:06.600 --> 33:09.560
I'm sorry, that is not escalation dominance.

33:09.560 --> 33:12.800
And furthermore, they needed the Americans.

33:12.800 --> 33:15.560
You all understand, I'm just sort of

33:16.640 --> 33:19.040
diverting from the path of mine for one second.

33:19.040 --> 33:21.640
If you look at what's happening in Gaza,

33:21.640 --> 33:25.520
the Israelis could never conduct that operation

33:25.520 --> 33:29.320
in Gaza without American support, not even close.

33:29.320 --> 33:31.520
And all sorts of Israeli generals say that

33:31.520 --> 33:32.640
in the Israeli press.

33:33.480 --> 33:37.680
They cannot by themselves produce the weaponry

33:37.680 --> 33:41.040
to conduct the operations they're now conducting in Gaza.

33:41.040 --> 33:42.000
They need us.

33:42.000 --> 33:45.000
And what I'm telling you about what happened

33:45.000 --> 33:47.840
on April 14th is they needed us.

33:49.160 --> 33:51.080
You hear all this talk about iron dome

33:51.080 --> 33:52.840
and their ability to shoot down missiles.

33:52.840 --> 33:54.560
They cannot do it alone.

33:54.560 --> 33:59.560
Iron dome is not that formidable defensive system

33:59.560 --> 34:01.960
and furthermore given cost exchange ratios,

34:01.960 --> 34:03.680
the number of missiles that the Iranians

34:03.680 --> 34:08.680
and Hezbollah have, iron dome over the long term

34:08.680 --> 34:11.920
in a fight is just not very useful.

34:11.920 --> 34:14.920
So from a deterrence point of view,

34:14.920 --> 34:16.920
the Israelis are in real trouble.

34:16.920 --> 34:18.680
So my first point is they're in real trouble

34:18.680 --> 34:20.200
because they're stuck in Gaza

34:20.200 --> 34:23.080
and they have no solution to the problem.

34:23.080 --> 34:28.080
And number two, their deterrence has been badly weakened.

34:28.920 --> 34:32.040
Number three is very important to understand

34:32.040 --> 34:33.720
with the coming of all these missiles

34:33.720 --> 34:35.680
and the coming of drones,

34:35.680 --> 34:38.960
it's now possible for actors like Hamas,

34:38.960 --> 34:42.920
the Houthis and Hezbollah and Iran

34:42.920 --> 34:47.920
to develop the capability to hit Israel

34:49.600 --> 34:52.480
and cause enormous amounts of damage.

34:52.480 --> 34:54.520
And lots of people who live in Israel

34:54.520 --> 34:57.480
are not very comfortable with this situation.

34:58.520 --> 35:02.360
The idea that they are exposed to adversaries

35:02.360 --> 35:04.480
and these are formidable adversaries.

35:04.480 --> 35:06.320
I don't wanna make light of the fact

35:06.320 --> 35:10.440
that groups like Hezbollah and groups like Hamas

35:10.440 --> 35:12.080
would like to finish Israel off.

35:12.080 --> 35:17.080
They would, these are really tough hombres.

35:17.440 --> 35:22.040
And what's happened here is that with the passage of time,

35:22.040 --> 35:24.680
missile capabilities and drone capabilities

35:24.680 --> 35:26.720
have reached the point where it's quite easy

35:26.720 --> 35:30.240
for actors like that to employ those weapons

35:30.240 --> 35:32.760
to create a real threat for Israel.

35:32.760 --> 35:36.200
The fourth way in which Israel is in trouble

35:36.200 --> 35:40.880
is that it has effectively become a pariah state

35:42.040 --> 35:45.600
in ways that it never was in the past.

35:45.600 --> 35:48.600
If you look at what's happening in the United States

35:48.600 --> 35:51.640
and all across the world on university campuses

35:51.640 --> 35:53.360
and college campuses,

35:53.360 --> 35:55.520
this is just evidence whether you think

35:55.520 --> 35:57.840
what's going on is right or wrong

35:57.840 --> 36:02.160
that Israel's reputation has been badly tarnished.

36:05.240 --> 36:10.240
If you think about the fact that South Africa took Israel

36:10.680 --> 36:14.400
before the International Court of Justice

36:14.400 --> 36:17.000
and the International Court of Justice found,

36:17.000 --> 36:20.160
not that Israel is committing genocide.

36:20.160 --> 36:21.400
They didn't find that.

36:21.400 --> 36:23.640
That is yet to be determined.

36:23.680 --> 36:26.600
But what the International Court of Justice did find

36:26.600 --> 36:28.960
is that there is sufficient evidence,

36:28.960 --> 36:32.640
there's enough evidence to think

36:32.640 --> 36:37.640
that Israel might be committing genocide.

36:37.760 --> 36:40.560
And if you look at polls inside the United States,

36:40.560 --> 36:43.920
it's truly remarkable how many people,

36:43.920 --> 36:45.680
especially Democrats,

36:45.680 --> 36:49.040
believed that Israel is engaged in genocide.

36:49.040 --> 36:50.880
There's a recent poll that shows

36:50.880 --> 36:55.320
that 56% of all Democrats think

36:55.320 --> 36:57.720
that Israel is committing genocide.

