Think about that, 56% of Americans

37:02.760 --> 37:06.120
hold think that Israel is committing genocide.

37:07.400 --> 37:09.720
There's another poll that shows,

37:09.720 --> 37:12.160
talks about Biden voters,

37:12.160 --> 37:17.160
that shows that 57% think Israel is committing genocide.

37:17.200 --> 37:21.320
27% are not sure.

