53:59.600 --> 54:02.200
in Gaza, who we talked about tonight,

54:02.200 --> 54:05.280
the Palestinians in the West Bank,

54:05.280 --> 54:07.600
and then the Palestinians inside of what's

54:07.600 --> 54:09.040
called Green Line Israel.

54:09.040 --> 54:14.520
That was the Israel that existed up until the 1967 war,

54:14.520 --> 54:20.560
before they captured those two territories.

54:20.560 --> 54:26.520
And when I say there are 7.3 million Palestinians

54:26.520 --> 54:29.560
in greater Israel, that includes the Palestinians

54:29.560 --> 54:32.400
in all three of those areas.

54:32.400 --> 54:35.680
The only Palestinians who can vote

54:35.680 --> 54:40.440
are the Palestinians in Green Line Israel.

54:40.440 --> 54:47.120
